</div>

<!-- SPLIT: LEFT IMAGE / RIGHT INFO -->
<div class="sh-split-section">
    <div class="sh-split">
        <div class="sh-split__img-wrap">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578662996442-48f60103fc96?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=85"
                 alt="Ship side view" />
            <span class="sh-split__img-label">MV Ocean Sovereign</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-split__info">
            <span class="kicker">On-Board Systems</span>
            <h2>World-Class <span>Capabilities</span></h2>
            <p>
                Every system aboard MV Ocean Sovereign has been selected to deliver peak
                reliability, operational flexibility and crew safety across the full spectrum
                of bulk cargo trades worldwide.
            </p>
            <p>
                From the advanced ECDIS navigation suite and Inmarsat Fleet One VSAT
                communications to the CO₂ fixed firefighting system and redundant steering
                gear, no compromises have been made in equipping this vessel for a lifetime
                of demanding global service.
            </p>
            <ul class="sh-split__checklist">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> ECDIS + AIS Class A</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Inmarsat VSAT</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> CO₂ Firefighting</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Hydraulic Hatch Covers</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> ECO Main Engine</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> SOLAS Lifeboats</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Bow Thruster 1,200 kW</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> BV Certified</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- HOVER TAB GALLERY -->
<div class="sh-tabs-section">
    <div class="section-head">
        <span class="kicker">Visual Tour</span>
        <h2>Explore the <span>Vessel</span></h2>
    </div>
